      "Certified QuickBooks ProAdvisor team",
      "Independent &middot; not Intuit",
      "Fixed-fee &middot; written scope in 3 days"
    ],
    "eyebrow": "New York &middot; Industry Accounting &middot; Built Around How You Run",
    "heading": "New York industry accounting &mdash; built around how your business runs.",
    "subheading": "Industry-specific accounting for New York businesses &mdash; construction, real estate, law firms, restaurants, healthcare, and nonprofits &mdash; configured around the number that runs each business, with New York&rsquo;s rules (NYC sales tax, the UBT, IOLTA, CHAR500) built in. Same named ProAdvisor, same fixed fee.",
    "actions": [
      { "label": "Book the discovery call", "href": "/contact/?intent=new-york&state=new-york&source_type=industry-index&funnel_stage=MOFU", "class": "btn--primary" },
      { "label": "Get the free file review", "href": "/quickbooks/file-review/?intent=file-review", "class": "btn--ghost" },
