    "source": "Reviewed by the Certified QuickBooks ProAdvisor team at TechBrot Inc., an independent firm &mdash; not affiliated with Intuit Inc. NY industry rules verified against NY DTF, the NY Attorney General Charities Bureau (CHAR500), and NY IOLTA Fund guidance."
  },
  "ctaBand": {
    "eyebrow": "Find your New York industry accountant",
    "heading": "Get accounting that fits your New York industry.",
    "lede": "Book a free discovery call. We&rsquo;ll review your QuickBooks file and the way your industry actually runs &mdash; with New York&rsquo;s rules included &mdash; and send a written fixed-fee quote within 3 business days. Independent firm &mdash; does not file NY/NYC taxes; coordinates with your CPA.",
